Title: Crushing the Crown
Description:
Looks like Hummel's got some security. But don't worry, I came with some special gifts to deliver.

<Snagglebolt points to the unmarked box.>

Bombs. I got bombs.

Playtime's over. Take those bombs and toss 'em at the Crown and their supplies. Let's give them a look at what genuine craftsmanship can do. Once we've cleared out their operations, we can move in on Hummel.
ObjectivesText: Use the Artisanal Bon-Bombs to destroy Crown supplies and kill Crown members.
